title: Jen Psaki, 2008 McCain Convention Lookback
itunes:title: Jen Psaki, 2008 McCain Convention Lookback
description:
Guests: Ryan Teague Beckwith, Bloomberg national political reporter, Jen Psaki, Former WH Communications Director for the Obama Administration, Rick Davis, Partner at Stone Court Capital, former campaign manager for John McCain's 2008 presidential campaign and Bloomberg Contributor, George Seay, CEO of Annandale Capital, Texas businessman, and former senior advisor to Marco Rubio's 2016 presidential campaign, and Luis Miranda, Former DNC Communications Director and Director of Communications And Politics at Alloy.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
